casebody.data:
Izudin DUBINOVIC, Plaintiff-Appellant,
v.
DES MOINES PUBLIC SCHOOLS, Defendant-Appellee. No. 18-1065 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed June 5, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

An employee appeals the district court ruling affirming the final agency action of the workers' compensation commissioner denying his claim for penalty benefits. AFFIRMED.

AFFIRMED.
